data.text:
2021 – 2022 Year of Dylan: The St. Louis County Board issued a proclamation making May 24, 2021, coinciding with Dylan’s 80th birthday, to May 24, 2022, the “Year of Dylan”.

Welcome to the new Dylan Way website: We are excited to welcome you to the new and updated Bob Dylan Way website, where you can be sure to find historical information about Bob Dylan, and his connections to Duluth, Minnesota.
